    <title>CodeForces构造算法（Constructive Algorithms）合集（一）</title>
    <link href="https://rabbit0121.github.io/2024/03/28/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/ConstructAlgorithm/CodeForces_ConstructAlgorithm_1/"/>
