    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!--@[TOC](CodeForces构造算法（Constructive Algorithms）合集（一）) --><h1 id="CF1948C-Path-Arrow"><a href="#CF1948C-Path-Arrow" class="headerlink" title="CF1948C Path Arrow"></a>CF1948C Path Arrow</h1><p>题目链接：<a href="https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1948/C">CF1948C Path Arrow</a></p><h2 id="大致题意"><a href="#大致题意" class="headerlink" title="大致题意"></a>大致题意</h2><p>给出一个由 ‘ &lt; ‘ 和 ‘ &gt; ‘ 组成的 $2×n$ 的地图，其中 ‘ &lt; ‘ 和 ‘ &gt; ‘ 代表前进方向，问机器人从 $(1,1)$ 出发能否到达 $(2,n)$ 处。</p><p>每秒钟，以下两个动作依次发生：</p><ul><li>首先，机器人向左、右、下或上移动 (它不能尝试走出网格，也不能跳过移动)；</li><li>然后沿着放置在当前单元格中的箭头移动（它在移动后停留在的单元格）</li></ul><p>输入的额外约束条件：</p><ul><li>$n$ 是偶数；</li><li>没有箭头指向网格外部；</li></ul><h2 id="解题思路"><a href="#解题思路" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><p>看到地图、到达 、最短步数等字眼应该想到BFS算法，将从当前位置出发，下一步可能到达的所有位置入队，如果在队空之前能到达目标点，输出 $YES$，否则输出 $NO$</p><span id="more"></span><p>需要注意的点：</p><ul><li>边界问题；</li><li>增加标记数组，在节点入队后及时标记，以免重复；</li><li>两个动作中有一个能到达即可。</li></ul><h2 id="实现代码"><a href="#实现代码" class="headerlink" title="实现代码"></a>实现代码</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> fx[<span class="number">4</span>][<span class="number">2</span>] = &#123;<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> t;</span><br><span class="line">    cin &gt;&gt; t;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (t--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> n;</span><br><span class="line">        cin &gt;&gt; n;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> flag[<span class="number">3</span>][n + <span class="number">10</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">memset</span>(flag, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(flag));</span><br><span class="line">        string s1[<span class="number">3</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        cin &gt;&gt; s1[<span class="number">1</span>] &gt;&gt; s1[<span class="number">2</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        s1[<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="string">&quot;a&quot;</span> + s1[<span class="number">1</span>];<span class="comment">//将下标调整为从1开始</span></span><br><span class="line">        s1[<span class="number">2</span>] = <span class="string">&quot;a&quot;</span> + s1[<span class="number">2</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        queue&lt;pair&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, <span class="type">int</span>&gt; &gt;q;</span><br><span class="line">        q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(&#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">        flag[<span class="number">1</span>][<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> temp = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> temp1 = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (!q.<span class="built_in">empty</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> nowx = q.<span class="built_in">front</span>().first;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> nowy = q.<span class="built_in">front</span>().second;</span><br><span class="line">            flag[nowx][nowy] = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            q.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//cout &lt;&lt; nowx &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; nowy &lt;&lt; endl;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (nowx == <span class="number">2</span> &amp;&amp; nowy == n) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;yes\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                temp = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="number">4</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">int</span> nextx = nowx + fx[i][<span class="number">0</span>];</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">int</span> nexty = nowy + fx[i][<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (nextx == <span class="number">2</span> &amp;&amp; nexty == n) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;yes\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                    temp1 = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                    temp = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (nextx &lt; <span class="number">1</span> || nextx &gt; <span class="number">2</span> || nexty &lt; <span class="number">1</span> || nexty &gt; n || flag[nextx][nexty] == <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">//cout &lt;&lt; nowx &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; nowy &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; nextx &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; nexty &lt;&lt; endl;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (s1[nextx ][nexty ] == <span class="string">&#x27;&gt;&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">if</span> (nexty + <span class="number">1</span> &lt;= n &amp;&amp; flag[nextx][nexty + <span class="number">1</span>] == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(&#123;nextx, nexty + <span class="number">1</span>&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">                        flag[nextx][nexty + <span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="comment">//cout &lt;&lt; nowx &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; nowy &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; nextx &lt;&lt; &quot; a&quot; &lt;&lt; nexty + 1 &lt;&lt; endl;</span></span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (s1[nextx ][nexty] == <span class="string">&#x27;&lt;&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">if</span> (nexty - <span class="number">1</span> &gt;= <span class="number">1</span> &amp;&amp; flag[nextx][nexty - <span class="number">1</span>] == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(&#123;nextx, nexty - <span class="number">1</span>&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">                        flag[nextx][nexty - <span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="comment">//cout &lt;&lt; nowx &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; nowy &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; nextx &lt;&lt; &quot; b&quot; &lt;&lt; nexty - 1 &lt;&lt; endl;</span></span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!temp1)</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//if(nowx==1)</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (temp)</span><br><span class="line">            cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;no\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="CF1948A-Special-Characters"><a href="#CF1948A-Special-Characters" class="headerlink" title="CF1948A Special Characters"></a>CF1948A Special Characters</h1><p>题目链接：<a href="https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1948/A">CF1948A Special Characters </a></p><h2 id="大致题意-1"><a href="#大致题意-1" class="headerlink" title="大致题意"></a>大致题意</h2><p>给定一个整数 $n$ ,构建一个由大写字母组成的字符串。这个字符串中恰好有 $n$ 个特殊字符。如果一个字符恰好等于它的邻居之一，我们称它为特殊字符。</p><p>若存在这样的字符串，输出任意一个，否则输出 $NO$ </p><h2 id="解题思路-1"><a href="#解题思路-1" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><p>注意特殊字符只能和一个相邻的字符相等</p><ul><li>假设第一个字母是 $A$ ，为了使它成为特殊字符，那么第二个字母只能是 $A$；</li><li>如果要使第二个字符成为特殊字符，由于它已经和第一个字符相等，那么第三个字符不能是 $A$，假设是$B$；</li><li>同理为使第三个字符成为特殊字符，第四个字符只能是 $B$ ；</li><li>以此类推…</li></ul><p>这样可以保证构造出来的字符串每个字符都是特殊字符。</p><p>感性理解：由于特殊字符都是成对出现，所以特殊字符的数量一定是偶数（严格的证明不会…多找几个例子应该可以发现这个规律）</p><h2 id="实现代码-1"><a href="#实现代码-1" class="headerlink" title="实现代码"></a>实现代码</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> t;cin&gt;&gt;t;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(t--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> n;cin&gt;&gt;n;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(n%<span class="number">2</span>==<span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;NO\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;YES\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;n;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span>(i%<span class="number">4</span>==<span class="number">0</span> || i%<span class="number">4</span>==<span class="number">1</span>) cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;A&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span> cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;B&quot;</span>; </span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="CF1944B-Equal-XOR"><a href="#CF1944B-Equal-XOR" class="headerlink" title="CF1944B Equal XOR"></a>CF1944B Equal XOR</h1><p>题目链接：<a href="https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1944/B">CF1944B Equal XOR </a></p><h2 id="大致题意-2"><a href="#大致题意-2" class="headerlink" title="大致题意"></a>大致题意</h2><ul><li>给定一个长度为 $2n$ 的数组，数组中从 $1$ 到 $n$ 的每个整数恰好出现两次；</li><li>给定一个整数 $k,(1 \leq k \leq \lfloor \frac{n}{2} \rfloor)$</li></ul><p>需要找到两个长度为 $2k$ 的数组 $l$ 和 $r$ ，使得：</p><ul><li>$l$ 是 $[a_1,a_2,…a_n]$ 的子集</li><li>$r$ 是 $[a_{n+1},a_{n+2},…a_{2n}]$ 的子集</li><li>$l$ 数组元素的按位异或等于数组 $r$ 的按位异或，即 $l_1 \oplus l_2 \oplus \cdots l_{2k}  &#x3D;r_1 \oplus r_2 \oplus \cdots r_{2k}$</li></ul><h2 id="解题思路-2"><a href="#解题思路-2" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><p>由于每个整数恰好出现两次，且相同的两个数异或为 $0$：</p><ul><li>如果有一个数在 $a_1\sim a_n$ 中出现两次，那么 $a_{n+1}\sim a_{2n}$ 中可能出现的数字种类最多为 $n-1$，那么由容斥原理必定有另一个数在 $a_{n+1}\sim a_{2n}$ 中出现两次；</li><li>如果有一个数在 $a_1\sim a_n$ 中出现一次，那么这个数在$a_{n+1}\sim a_{2n}$ 中也出现一次。</li></ul><p>可以统计每个数在 $a_1\sim a_n$ 中出现的次数：</p><ul><li>数组 $l$：先依次输出出现 $2$ 次的，再输出出现 $1$ 次的；</li><li>数组 $r$：先依次输出出现 $0$ 次的，再输出出现 $1$ 次的。</li></ul><h2 id="实现代码-2"><a href="#实现代码-2" class="headerlink" title="实现代码"></a>实现代码</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> t;cin&gt;&gt;t;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(t--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> n,k;cin&gt;&gt;n&gt;&gt;k;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> a[<span class="number">2</span>*n+<span class="number">10</span>],cnt[<span class="number">2</span>*n+<span class="number">10</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">memset</span>(cnt,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(cnt));</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=<span class="number">2</span>*n;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            cin&gt;&gt;a[i];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(i&lt;=n) cnt[a[i]]++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> cnt1=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(cnt[i]==<span class="number">2</span> &amp;&amp; cnt1+<span class="number">2</span>&lt;=<span class="number">2</span>*k) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout&lt;&lt;i&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;i&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                cnt1+=<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(cnt[i]==<span class="number">1</span> &amp;&amp; cnt1+<span class="number">1</span>&lt;=<span class="number">2</span>*k) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout&lt;&lt;i&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                cnt1+=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;cnt1=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(cnt[i]==<span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; cnt1+<span class="number">2</span>&lt;=<span class="number">2</span>*k) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout&lt;&lt;i&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;i&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                cnt1+=<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(cnt[i]==<span class="number">1</span> &amp;&amp; cnt1+<span class="number">1</span>&lt;=<span class="number">2</span>*k) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout&lt;&lt;i&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                cnt1+=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="CF1935B-Informatics-in-MAC"><a href="#CF1935B-Informatics-in-MAC" class="headerlink" title="CF1935B Informatics in MAC"></a>CF1935B Informatics in MAC</h1><p>题目链接：<a href="https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1935/B">CF1935B Informatics in MAC </a></p><h2 id="大致题意-3"><a href="#大致题意-3" class="headerlink" title="大致题意"></a>大致题意</h2><p>给定一个长度为 $n$ 的数组，将其分成 $k&gt;1$个子段 $(l_i \sim r_i, i \in(1,k))$，使得每个子段上的 $\mathbf{MEX}$ 都等于同一个整数。如果存在这样的划分，输出任意一个，否则输出 $-1$.</p><ul><li>$\mathbf{MEX}$：不属于数组的最小非负整数。</li></ul><h2 id="解题思路-3"><a href="#解题思路-3" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><ul><li>如果有两个相邻区间的 $\mathbf{MEX}$ 相等，那么两个相邻区间可以合并为一个区间，所以如果存在这样的划分，那么最后一定可以合并成只剩 $2$ 个区间；</li><li>暴力求出 $lesft$ 和 $right$：其中 $right[i]$： $1 \sim i, i \in [1,n]$ 区间的 $\mathbf{MEX}$ ，$left[i]$：$i \sim n, i \in [1,n]$ 区间的 $\mathbf{MEX}$；</li><li>从前往后描找到符合条件的 $i$，使得 $left[i+1] &#x3D; right[i]$ 即为所求，如果找不到，那么说明不存在这样的划分。</li></ul><h2 id="实现代码-3"><a href="#实现代码-3" class="headerlink" title="实现代码"></a>实现代码</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> maxsize 100005</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> right1[maxsize],left1[maxsize],num[maxsize];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> flag[maxsize];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> t;cin&gt;&gt;t;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(t--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> n;cin&gt;&gt;n;<span class="built_in">memset</span>(flag,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(flag));</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;n;i++) cin&gt;&gt;num[i];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> now=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;n;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            flag[num[i]]=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span>(flag[now]==<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                now++;</span><br><span class="line">            right1[i]=now;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        now=<span class="number">0</span>;<span class="built_in">memset</span>(flag,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(flag));</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=n<span class="number">-1</span>;i&gt;=<span class="number">0</span>;i--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            flag[num[i]]=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span>(flag[now]==<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                now++;</span><br><span class="line">            left1[i]=now;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//        for(int i=0;i&lt;n;i++) &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//            cout&lt;&lt;right1[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;&lt;&lt;left1[i]&lt;&lt;&quot;\n&quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//        &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        now=<span class="number">0</span>;<span class="type">int</span> ans=<span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;n<span class="number">-1</span>;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(right1[i]==left1[i+<span class="number">1</span>]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;2\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;1 &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;i+<span class="number">1</span>&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">                cout&lt;&lt;i+<span class="number">2</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;n&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                ans=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(ans==<span class="number">-1</span>) cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;-1\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;                        </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="CF1935A-Entertainment-in-MAC"><a href="#CF1935A-Entertainment-in-MAC" class="headerlink" title="CF1935A Entertainment in MAC"></a>CF1935A Entertainment in MAC</h1><p>题目链接：<a href="https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1935/A">CF1935A Entertainment in MAC </a></p><h2 id="大致题意-4"><a href="#大致题意-4" class="headerlink" title="大致题意"></a>大致题意</h2><p>给定一个字符串 $s$ 和一个偶数$n$，你可以对它应用两种操作：</p><ul><li>将反转后的字符串 $s$ 添加到字符串 $s$ 的末尾。例如：如果 $s$ &#x3D; cpm，那么应用操作后 $s$ &#x3D; cpmmpc</li><li>反转当前字符串 $s$。例如：如果 $s$ &#x3D; cpm，那么应用操作后 $s$ &#x3D; mpc</li></ul><p>输出使用 $n$ 次操作后可以获得的最小字典序的字符串</p><h2 id="解题思路-4"><a href="#解题思路-4" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><p>操作涉及到反转，应该可以想到回文串，由操作 $1$ 和 $2$ 可以得出：</p><ul><li>执行一次操作 $1$ 会将字符串变成回文串；</li><li>执行一次操作 $2$ 会将字符串反转；</li><li>对回文串执行操作 $1$ 相当于将回文串延长一倍；</li><li>对回文串执行操作 $2$ 对字符串本身没有影响。</li></ul><p>因此我们可以比较原字符串和反转后的字符串的字典序（记为 $s’$&#x3D;$s_{n}, s_{n-1} \cdots  s_2 , s_1$）</p><ul><li>如果 $s \leq s’$，输出原字符串；</li><li>如果 $s &gt; s’$，输出反转后的字符串。</li></ul><h2 id="实现代码-4"><a href="#实现代码-4" class="headerlink" title="实现代码"></a>实现代码</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> t;cin&gt;&gt;t;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(t--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> n;cin&gt;&gt;n;</span><br><span class="line">        string s;cin&gt;&gt;s;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">bool</span> flag=<span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;s.<span class="built_in">length</span>();i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(s[i]==s[s.<span class="built_in">length</span>()<span class="number">-1</span>-i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(s[i]&gt;s[s.<span class="built_in">length</span>()<span class="number">-1</span>-i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                flag=<span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(s[i]&lt;s[s.<span class="built_in">length</span>()<span class="number">-1</span>-i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                flag=<span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(!flag) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=s.<span class="built_in">length</span>()<span class="number">-1</span>;i&gt;=<span class="number">0</span>;i--) cout&lt;&lt;s[i];</span><br><span class="line">            cout&lt;&lt;s&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> cout&lt;&lt;s&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;                        </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;!--@[TOC](CodeForces构造算法（Constructive Algorithms）合集（一）) --&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;CF1948C-Path-Arrow&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#CF1948C-Path-Arrow&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;CF1948C Path Arrow&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;CF1948C Path Arrow&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目链接：&lt;a href=&quot;https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1948/C&quot;&gt;CF1948C Path Arrow&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;大致题意&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#大致题意&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;大致题意&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;大致题意&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;给出一个由 ‘ &amp;lt; ‘ 和 ‘ &amp;gt; ‘ 组成的 $2×n$ 的地图，其中 ‘ &amp;lt; ‘ 和 ‘ &amp;gt; ‘ 代表前进方向，问机器人从 $(1,1)$ 出发能否到达 $(2,n)$ 处。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;每秒钟，以下两个动作依次发生：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;首先，机器人向左、右、下或上移动 (它不能尝试走出网格，也不能跳过移动)；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;然后沿着放置在当前单元格中的箭头移动（它在移动后停留在的单元格）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;输入的额外约束条件：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;$n$ 是偶数；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;没有箭头指向网格外部；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;解题思路&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#解题思路&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;解题思路&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;解题思路&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;看到地图、到达 、最短步数等字眼应该想到BFS算法，将从当前位置出发，下一步可能到达的所有位置入队，如果在队空之前能到达目标点，输出 $YES$，否则输出 $NO$&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
